snippet.title: Counterpick Labs - Open Alpha Trailer
snippet.description:
Counterpick Labs is a free, browser-based platform fighter featuring rollback netcode and modular character customization. Monetization is cosmetic only (no pay-to-win).
Play the game at https://www.counterpicklabs.com/
Join the discord: https://discord.gg/z9jGz6f77H

Music: "Now Loading From Disk" by Steven O'Brien (steven-obrien.net)
